"title": "6139: deadness, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6139: deadness, spiritual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Being morally and spiritually without life, therefore without a relationship with God. This condition, being the result of original sin, brings wrath and judgment and can be changed only by the sovereign, intervening grace of God.</p>\n<h2>Spiritual deadness is humanity's condition by nature</h2>\n<h3>It is linked to physical death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:3\">GEN 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:19\">GEN 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:19\">PRO 11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:20-Ezek18:31\">EZK 18:20–18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:21-John8:24\">JHN 8:21–8:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:32\">ROM 1:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></p>\n<h3>It is the universal consequence of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1\">EPH 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:21\">GEN 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13\">1CH 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:5\">PSA 51:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:3\">PSA 58:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:16\">PRO 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:53\">JHN 6:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:13\">ROM 5:12–5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:17\">ROM 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>It is confirmed in the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:20\">ROM 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4-Rom7:12\">ROM 7:4–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:2-Rom8:4\">ROM 8:2–8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:19\">GAL 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>It is evidenced in the human mind</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:21\">COL 1:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:15\">TIT 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>It is evidenced in the human body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24\">ROM 7:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:12-Rom6:14\">ROM 6:12–6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16\">ROM 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10\">ROM 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:50\">1CO 15:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7-Gal6:8\">GAL 6:7–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22\">EPH 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:6\">1TI 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:6\">JAS 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual darkness brings judgment</h2>\n<h3>God's judgment is final</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:26\">LUK 16:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:24\">ISA 66:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:30-Matt25:32\">MAT 25:30–25:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43-Mark9:49\">MRK 9:43–9:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:28\">LUK 13:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:17\">1PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>The second death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:14-Rev20:15\">REV 20:14–20:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:16-1John5:17\">1JN 5:16–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">JUD 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a></p>\n<h2>Rescue from spiritual deadness is initiated by God</h2>\n<h3>He brings salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:12\">PSA 103:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">ISA 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1-Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:1–37:14</a></p>\n<h3>He brings union with the death of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:4\">ROM 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:5-Rom6:10\">ROM 6:5–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10\">2CO 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:15-2Cor5:17\">2CO 5:15–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:19-Gal2:20\">GAL 2:19–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:14\">GAL 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12\">COL 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>He brings union with the resurrection of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1\">COL 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:21\">ROM 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:11\">ROM 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:4-Rev20:5\">REV 20:4–20:5</a></p>\n<h3>He brings ultimate physical resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10-Rom8:11\">ROM 8:10–8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:42–15:49</a></p>\n<h2>Concern for those who are spiritually sleepy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:14\">EPH 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:11\">ROM 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:5-1Thess5:7\">1TH 5:5–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1-Rev3:2\">REV 3:1–3:2</a></p>",
